h=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Residential Property Service:</strong></h3>\r\nWe have a wide experience in sale, purchase of residential properties. We have a database of various clients who want to sell or buy properties. We identify and understand the need of our clients and help them in finding a suitable property, which suits there necessity and budget. We maintain privacy about buyers/sellers and conclude the deal at the best market prices. We offer flexible and comprehensive range of services and considerable knowledge of the market place. Our experience will ensure that you are in safe hands, if you are buying and selling any residential property.\r\n<h3><strong>Commercial Property Service:</strong></h3>\r\nWe have a wide experience in sale, purchase of commercial properties. As it is know that it is the era of Commercial Malls, Cine multiplex, Amusement parks, Software parks etc. We identify and understand the need of our clients and help them in finding a suitable commercial land for establishing their business according to their budget. With our professional and dedicated team, we endeavor to make the world a better place. We intend to provide a more prosperous, safer and stable future for you business needs.\r\n<h3><strong>Agricultural Property Service:</strong></h3>\r\nWe have complete real estate representative offers complete solution for various agricultural properties. Our knowledge, experience and manpower had resulted in some of the big agricultural property dealing in U.P, Delhi and NCR. The property demand in this location is increasing day by day due to its nearness to the national capital. If you want to earn profit try to invest in these prime areas. Our experts have calculated that property rate is increasing rapidly and investing in agriculture land is very sound idea. So if you want to know more about the property land, locations, prices feel free to contact us at any time. Our experts will entertain your queries to resolve all issues.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Buying & Selling Properties','','publish','closed','closed','','buying-selling-properties','','','2015-12-24 12:34:27','2015-12-24 12:34:27','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?page_id=161',0,'page','',0),(162,1,'2015-12-12 09:19:41','2015-12-12 09:19:41','Coming Soon!','Buying & Selling Properties','','inherit','closed','closed','','161-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:19:41','2015-12-12 09:19:41','',161,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/161-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(164,1,'2015-12-12 09:20:31','2015-12-12 09:20:31','Coming Soon!','Property Management','','publish','closed','closed','','property-management','','','2015-12-19 06:40:59','2015-12-19 06:40:59','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?page_id=164',0,'page','',0),(165,1,'2015-12-12 09:20:31','2015-12-12 09:20:31','Coming Soon!','Property Management','','inherit','closed','closed','','164-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:20:31','2015-12-12 09:20:31','',164,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/164-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(166,1,'2015-12-12 09:21:09','2015-12-12 09:21:09','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2><strong>Vastu Consultant for House, Office, Business etc</strong></h2>\r\nVastu shastra unifies the science, art,astronomy and astrology. it can also be said as an ancient mystic science for designs and building. Vastu shastra helps us to make our lives better and will secure from things going wrong.Vastu Expert considered the interplay of various forces of nature involving the five elements of earth, water,wind, fire and these elements guide and changes the living styles of not only human being but every living being on earth.. Thus they influence our deeds, luck,behavior and other basics of life. Vastu beleives that there are essentially two types of forces which are equal and opposite in nature.\r\n\r\nThe interection of these two forces is cosmosic.Vastu means proper place to live in. it should be habitatable. It is prayers to vaastu purusha and means oh god of structures and building. We are your devotees. Listen our prayers, make us free of disease. Give wealth and prosperity, help the well being of all persons and animals living in the house. vastu shastra is applicable;e in all plots, flat , offices , houses, home and commercial buildings. These all are applied by the vastu consultant.\r\n\r\nAstrology is all about prediction of some zodiacs and planets and on other side Vastu Shastra is mainly focus on directions and positive or negative energy around us. This Shastra is very important when you construct a new architecture. You have to fulfill all conditions of Vastu Shastra and design the house according Vastu directions. If you not follow the instructions of this Shastra then you face problems every day.\r\n\r\nToday every person believe in Vastu Shastra and they aware about the damage if they don’t follow this. If you build up a new building or house then our best Vastu consultant advised you how to design the building and which part of come first and which are last. Our Vastu Expert Dr.XXX provides their services in every city of India. There services are in various cities like Hyderabad, Chennai, Goa and Pune. They attend so many seminars in Chennai. They are expert in Vastu Jyotisha and provide you solution for every problem.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Vastu Consultant','','publish','closed','closed','','vastu-consultant','','','2015-12-24 12:45:53','2015-12-24 12:45:53','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?page_id=166',0,'page','',0),(167,1,'2015-12-12 09:21:09','2015-12-12 09:21:09','Coming Soon!','Vastu Consultant','','inherit','closed','closed','','166-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:21:09','2015-12-12 09:21:09','',166,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/166-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(168,1,'2015-12-12 09:22:04','2015-12-12 09:22:04','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Interior Architecture and Design</strong></h3>\r\nInterior spaces have the ability to generate value on a wide variety of organizational and human fronts, including productivity, health and well-being, and purchasing potential. Drawing from our broad expertise in architecture, technology and systems, branding and environments, our interior architects and designers work across geographies and sectors to create memorable and meaningful places that support operational objectives, create value and improve quality of life.\r\n<h5>Residential Interior Design:</h5>\r\n<strong>Modular Kitchen</strong>: Modular Kitchens are the order of the day in an era that focuses on convenience, space economy and utility value. Our Modular Kitchens cater to these requirement    s as they are combinations of futuristic features put together into a compact format. These are tailored to suit the customer’s requirements in terms of their building, applications, durability, usage and elegance.\r\n\r\nModular Kitchen is fast becoming an integral part of a home. The growing preference to have modular kitchen, in the place of conventional kitchen, is due to the fact that Modular kitchen offers convenience, aesthetics and optimum space utilization. It helps the housewife in tackling the cooking chores with less work. The space management is derived through use of horizontal and vertical space. Good storage practice prevents ants, insects and cockroaches from getting into food articles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bed Room</strong>\r\n\r\nThe bedroom is that part of the house where we go to recharge and rest after a hard day’s work and the daily stress. To do so, the room must be similar to our personality to make us feel the way we should be, but it should also be designed with style, without crowding it with useless materials that would remove the idea of spacious special retreat.\r\nMany people think they know how to create a good bedroom interior design, but can they make it great? In these following pictures, there are 40 modern interior design ideas that should inspire you. Surely, some of them are a little bit exotic but you need to have something to hope for. Besides the luxurious interior design styles, you will also find some down to earth ones that you could apply to your bedroom when redesigning it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Living Room</strong>\r\n\r\n\"The Living Room you\'ve always wanted begins here! From classy sofa cum beds, sofa sets, to dining tables, we\'ve got it all. All our living room furniture is made to order. So after you pick a style that suits your lifestyle, you also get to pick from over 5 polish options and over 500 fabric samples. Need something made to a specific size? No problem!! Your stylish, made to order, hassle-free, affordable home is here. Visit any of our showrooms and come explore your options.\"\r\n\r\n<strong>False Ceiling</strong>\r\n\r\nWe at STARK INTERIO offer a wide galore of enthralling False Ceilings that enhances the beauty of your homes, offices, showrooms and corporate offices. The false ceiling enlivens the look of homes. offices &amp; showrooms. Our company creates a variety of False Ceilings such as Gypboard False Ceilings, Thermocole False Ceiling and Grid False ceiling.\r\n\r\nWe are the designers of an exquisite array of False Ceiling and Gypsum Partitions like Gypsum False Ceiling. Thermocole False Ceiling which are widely used in commercial as well as residential buildings. Their installation gives pleasing appearance to the residential and commercial building. We have a wide range of False Ceilings to make your home or office more attractive and appealing at a reasonable cost. There are many types that are accessible and can be applied to your room ceiling or office.\r\n\r\n<strong>Wall Panelling</strong>\r\n\r\nFeel like changing your interior? Need to renovate your interior? Discover Grosfillex EXAPAN panelling, a simple and decorative solution for dressing your walls. Whether your interior is contemporary, authentic, natural or tonic, the Grosfillex panelling collections cover all tastes and will adapt to all rooms in the home. Grosfillex know-how combined with the properties of PVC, make for easy installation and an impeccable, long-lasting result.\r\n<h3>Corporate Interior Design:</h3>\r\n<strong>Interior Designs</strong>\r\n\r\nOur company is one of the very well known companies in the area of interior designs. We are offering various type of interior decoration for offices. We are offering an exclusive look to the office which looks very attractive and exclusive. Our company provides top class service or different range of colors combination, textures, fabrics, furniture for the space of office interior. We are offering the interior for offices with an affordable price.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cabin Management Designs</strong>\r\n\r\nWell designed Office Cabin Management Designs represent the work culture of any organization and builds up its image in the mind of employees. We have excellence of designing the workstations, which suit the surroundings of the organization and make a great impact on the people. From conceptualization to designing and installation of all necessary furnishing items, each and every activity for developing the workstations is conducted under the close observation of experienced designers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Meeting Rooms</strong>\r\n\r\nDesigning of meetingroom is a a serious challenge, as it reflects the values and status of company in front of its prospective clients. Our adept designers are well versed with the designing concepts of these rooms and undertake the interior decoration of board rooms for various popular corporate clients. Color shades of wall, ceiling &amp; floor, furnishing of lighting, blind, curtains, furniture and other decorative items, each aspect of the rooms is refurbished by our designers and given a breathtaking and professional look. While designing these rooms, we pay meticulous attention, that this designing suits the specifications and demands of our clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>Conference Rooms</strong>\r\n\r\nConference room is a place where employer and staff gather to appoint a meeting and hence it should be designed in a formal style which must communicate with the company image and values. Conference room requires simple aesthetic interiors coordinating with colour palate and material. This room is not for every staff member present in office arena while it is just for main heads and executives so the ambience of the room should depend on the clientele and type of business.\r\n\r\n<strong>Aluminium Composite Panel Cladding Works</strong>\r\n\r\nACP Cladding solutions offered comprise aluminum composite panel based cladding solutions that are made available with wide range of color options to choose from. Designed to provide for desired aesthetic elevation, it helps in enhancing the look of the buildings and widely find usage for meeting the demands of external cladding of buildings.\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotels</strong>\r\n\r\nCreating an exotic milieu in the hospitality industries, our interior designing services are availed by leading hotels and restaurants. While designing the interior of hotel lobbies, our designers keep into mind various factors such as clients\' budget, optimization of flooring space etc and furnish qualitative as well as luxurious furniture, lighting, wall decorations and other essential items, which lend them an eye catching and sumptuous look. Apart from this, we also provide interior designing consultancy services to our clients.\r\n<strong>Resorts</strong>\r\n\r\nResorts and villas are renowned for offering celebrities and wealthy globe-trotters trendy and abundant facilities for rest, recreation and fine wining &amp; dining. A lavish resort can be anything – a hill resort, beach resort, and water resort – anywhere with breathtaking views of natural scenic beauties. A lavish resort includes vast tracts of lands – sometimes as big as a whole village size – often as large as 1500-2000 acres.\r\n\r\n<strong>Restaurants</strong>\r\n\r\nThe impressive interior designing of hotels and restaurant interior design can assist them to attract large numbers of guests. We possess a deep knowledge of hotel and restaurant designing to provide maximum functionality without compromising on aesthetic looks. Our restaurant interior design services add sophistication and charm to reception room, cafe, swimming pools, bars, discotheques, entertainment zones and many other areas. While jazzing up the interior of these restaurants, we keep in mind color shades, false ceiling, flooring, lighting and other various factors.\r\n\r\n<strong>Renovation Interiors</strong>\r\nWe undertake all kinds of Renovation works that include Civil, Electrical, Plumbing, Tiling/Flooring, carpentry and Painting/polishing works. We offer designs based on elements of Vasthu and the requirements of the clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>Civil</strong>: Demolition of walls, construction of new walls, extension of roof with necessary foundations, kitchen platforms etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Electrical</strong>:  New wiring, Distribution boards, switch gear, telephone wiring and networking.\r\n\r\n<strong>Plumbing</strong>:  New lines, shifting and fixing of sanitaryware and CP fittings\r\n\r\n<strong>Tiling/Flooring</strong>: In Vitrified, ceramic, glazed, Marble, Granite, Kota, Shahabad stones etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Carpentry</strong>:  Alteration and making of new doors and windows with frames, wardrobes, lofts, kitchen cabinets etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Painting</strong>:  Repainting the walls, doors, windows and grills using high quality paints and in colors that suit the ambience.\r\n\r\n<strong>Home Renovation Specialist:</strong>\r\nOur Sales staff will introduce our company to you and advice you about your options and cost. Then will send quotation for the service that you have hoped for.\r\n\r\nThird the design team will produce the architectural drawings, assists you with product selections and ensures that your requirements are met.\r\n\r\nThen we will assign a project manager to liaise between you and our entire dedicated team to make sure your renovation progresses as smoothly as possible.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Architect & Interior Design','','publish','closed','closed','','architect-interior-design','','','2015-12-24 12:33:35','2015-12-24 12:33:35','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?page_id=168',0,'page','',0),(169,1,'2015-12-12 09:22:04','2015-12-12 09:22:04','Coming Soon!','Architect & Interior Design','','inherit','closed','closed','','168-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:22:04','2015-12-12 09:22:04','',168,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/168-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(170,1,'2015-12-12 09:22:33','2015-12-12 09:22:33','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Property Loan Consultant\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Property Loan Consultant:</strong></h3>\r\nThe property prices are always sky-rocketing in Andhra Pradesh if you don’t have funds to buy the property you want, availing Property loans is a good option. We are a Andhra Pradesh based credible Property Loan Consultant and have links with financial institutions like ICICI bank, HDFC bank, PNB, Indiabulls, DHFL and LIC.\r\n\r\nWe can assist you in getting loans such as commercial property loan, residential property loan, home loan and loan against property. With our assistance you will have a hassle free time in availing the loan and at a low rate of interest.\r\n\r\n<strong>Home Loan</strong>\r\n\r\nHome loan is a secured loan given to individuals who aspire to build or buy a house. The property so purchased is mortgaged in the name of the lending institution as security, till the time the loan is fully repaid.\r\n\r\nThe lending institution will hold the original property related documents till the time the loan is fully repaid along with the interest.\r\n\r\nTo buy a house, be it under construction, ready or resale property, the residence buyer can seek for loan from banks or financial institutions through financial advisors or home loan agents.\r\n\r\nIt should be noted that the terms and conditions of the housing loan can differ widely in terms of loan amount, maturity period, interest rate, repayment mode, etc.\r\n\r\nRANKPROPERTIES Consultancy has been working in this arena for several years as home loan advisors and home loan agents. We have expertise in identifying the banks and institutions that offer the loan on most friendly terms. Till date, we have been instrumental and successful home loan advisors in Mumbai providing home loans to salaried individuals, self employed, professionals and NRIs to procure home loans at best terms.\r\n\r\nOur home loan advisors strive to provide you the home loan deals at the cheapest rate of interest.\r\n\r\n<strong>Home loans to</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Salaried Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Self Employed Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Individual</li>\r\n	<li>NRI\'s</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Loan amount &amp; Loan Tenure</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>From 10 Lacs to 10 Crore</li>\r\n	<li>Decided on Market Value of Property</li>\r\n	<li>Decided on repaying capacity of the borrower basis income documents</li>\r\n	<li>5 yrs to 15/20 yrs – for Self Employed</li>\r\n	<li>5 yrs to 20/25 yrs – for professional &amp; Salaried</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Mortgage Loan</strong>\r\n\r\nMortgage loan or loan against property means the borrower takes a loan which is secured against his current residential or commercial property. The benefit of mortgage loan is that it considers the market value of the property as on date. As such, the borrower can get higher amounts of loan. Best is, the loan money can be used to meet financials requirements of any kind.\r\n\r\n<strong>Loan Against Property to</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Salaried Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Self Employed Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Individual</li>\r\n	<li>NRI\'s</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Why loan against property?</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Working capital requirement</li>\r\n	<li>To fill short term financial requirement</li>\r\n	<li>Business Expansion</li>\r\n	<li>To set up new business</li>\r\n	<li>Debt Consolidation</li>\r\n	<li>Home Extension or Renovation</li>\r\n	<li>Marriage, Travel or Education</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Property Loan Consultant','','publish','closed','closed','','property-loan-consultant','','','2015-12-24 12:38:36','2015-12-24 12:38:36','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?page_id=170',0,'page','',0),(171,1,'2015-12-12 09:22:33','2015-12-12 09:22:33','Coming Soon!','Property Loan Consultant','','inherit','closed','closed','','170-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:22:33','2015-12-12 09:22:33','',170,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/170-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(172,1,'2015-12-12 09:23:04','2015-12-12 09:23:04','Contents about buying properties','Buying Properties','','inherit','closed','closed','','44-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:23:04','2015-12-12 09:23:04','',44,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/44-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(173,1,'2015-12-12 09:23:14','2015-12-12 09:23:14','Coming Soon!','Buying Properties','','inherit','closed','closed','','44-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:23:14','2015-12-12 09:23:14','',44,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/44-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(174,1,'2015-12-12 09:23:42','2015-12-12 09:23:42','Selling Properties','Selling Properties','','inherit','closed','closed','','46-revision-v1','','','2015-12-12 09:23:42','2015-12-12 09:23:42','',46,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/2015/12/12/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(175,1,'2015-12-12 09:27:30','2015-12-12 09:27:30',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','175','','','2016-01-02 09:58: