omplex real estate issues into opportunities for growth. From business owners and investors to lenders and corporate groups, we offer you the experience, know-how, and the strategic planning that helps lead to better decisions. Our range of services includes: Due diligence, market studies, portfolio services, lease advisory, and more. Virtually everything you need to enhance the value of your business, you’ll find at RankProperties.\r\n\r\n•    Real Estate Due Diligence\r\n•    Real Estate Market Studies\r\n•    Portfolio Services\r\n•    Lease Advisory\r\n\r\n<strong>PORTFOLIO MANAGEMENT:</strong>\r\n\r\nAt RANKPROPERTIES, we advise and manage real estate investments for our clients in various locations and across asset classes. Our real estate advisors in Chennai assists companies and high net worth individuals to manage lease, buy/sell ,develop/re-develop captive residential and commercial real estate, including large or small land parcels with a clear time-bound approach, by engaging prospective buyers / investors / developers / IPCs all on a case-to-case basis.\r\n\r\nWe manage your real estate investments as a Complete Real Estate Portfolio, linking it with your overall financial planning goals. Our real estate investment advisors can structure your assets as an income generating portfolio or an aggressive real estate portfolio for wealth creation.\r\n\r\n<strong>Objectives and Essence:</strong>\r\n\r\nThe objective of RANKPROPERTIES\'s real estate portfolio management is to ensure that the entrusted estate portfolio is managed with the best business practices and in compliance with the current legal and regulatory framework. The essence is to add value to the investment or disinvestment process with a high degree of active engagement.\r\n\r\n<strong>TRANSACTION ADVISORY SERVICES</strong>\r\n\r\nDecisions related to real estate investments need meticulous thought and robust advice. RANKPROPERTIES offers a gamut of real estate advisory services, customized to the clients\' requirements. Our expert advisors will manage your real estate investment portfolio and provide the right property advisory services. Our market research team is abreast with the evolving trends in Chennai real estate. With profound knowledge and information, we provide you with solid recommendations according to the changes in trends, to develop action plans that align with your objectives.\r\n\r\nWe offer real estate services to residential as well as institutional and commercial properties. We can suggest innovative methods of divestitures and partnerships to create diverse investment portfolios for our clients. We optimize the options available with a wide range of real estate investment opportunities that are at par with the stake holders\' expectations. We manage your assets according to your preferences and interests and ensure positive results out of them.\r\n\r\nBacked by a treasure of knowledge and experience, we provide holistic Property Advisory Services, understanding the potential of the property at hand. We have in-depth knowledge of Chennai real estate and thus, are able to provide you with accurate and strategic suggestions. Our services span over both asset acquisition and asset disposition. RANKPROPERTIES team will have a talk with you, understand your needs and then, offer you the best return on investment.\r\n\r\n<strong>a. Asset Acquisition Services</strong>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES has an excellent track record in buying and selling real estate property, despite the complicated laws of the land, governing acquisition. Our experts are at your service to simplify the tedious legal process and paper work. Our experts assist you to understand the legal jargons, technicalities and to coordinate between the seller and other stake holders to quickly close the process, thus making buying and selling property, effortless. Legal assistance to scrutinize the title deed and relevant documents to ascertain ownership and marketability are done by a panel of experts and findings shared with the buyer. Assessments pertaining to approachability, location details, status of land/building under construction etc. are reported. Another service that most clients look forward to is the scrutiny of the documents provided by the seller. Our real estate consultants go ahead and verify the authenticity of all documents pertaining to the real estate/property to identify the genuineness of the transaction. Where there is a POA (Power of Attorney), we assist the holder in executing the registration in the name of the owner. Sale deeds and agreements required for bank loans and other financial assistance are drafted and negotiations with these institutions are done by our experts at RANKPROPERTIES. The process is then taken to closure after getting the property registered in the name of the buyer. Post purchase services include transfer to documents to the current owner. Service charges are applicable on the above services. Our dedicated team of real estate legal advisors and managers are committed to demonstrate effective results. We are partnered with the best law firms that give us valuable advice relating to real estate law, which is essential part of property and project management.\r\n\r\n<strong>b.    Asset Disposition</strong>\r\nRANKPROPERTIES offers selling assistance to owners of real estate property, plots, commercial establishments and retail space. To ensure that we meet client expectations, our panel of real estate consultants and legal advisors work together seamlessly to make the sale a success. Our experts involve themselves on behalf of you, in the sale transaction, to largely safe guard your interest and to ensure smooth transition. Their tactful involvement will ensure execution of the sale deed as per the sellers’ requirements. Our real estate legal advisors then proceed to channelize their expertise to get the property registered by executing the sale deed. Our responsibility does not end with this. We ensure that your documents are procured and the registration is complete on the predetermined day. Transfer of documents in your name and other post registration activities are completed and documents handed over to you for safe keeping.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Real Estate Consultant','','inherit','closed','closed','','63-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 10:54:07','2015-12-18 10:54:07','',63,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/63-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(254,1,'2015-12-18 10:58:04','2015-12-18 10:58:04','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Property Loan Consultant\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\n\nI am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Property Loan Consultant','','inherit','closed','closed','','170-autosave-v1','','','2015-12-18 10:58:04','2015-12-18 10:58:04','',170,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/170-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(255,1,'2015-12-18 11:00:58','2015-12-18 11:00:58','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Property Loan Consultant\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Property Loan Consultant:</strong></h3>\r\nThe property prices are always sky-rocketing in Andhra Pradesh if you don’t have funds to buy the property you want, availing Property loans is a good option. We are a Andhra Pradesh based credible Property Loan Consultant and have links with financial institutions like ICICI bank, HDFC bank, PNB, Indiabulls, DHFL and LIC.\r\n\r\nWe can assist you in getting loans such as commercial property loan, residential property loan, home loan and loan against property. With our assistance you will have a hassle free time in availing the loan and at a low rate of interest.\r\n\r\n<strong>Home Loan</strong>\r\n\r\nHome loan is a secured loan given to individuals who aspire to build or buy a house. The property so purchased is mortgaged in the name of the lending institution as security, till the time the loan is fully repaid.\r\n\r\nThe lending institution will hold the original property related documents till the time the loan is fully repaid along with the interest.\r\n\r\nTo buy a house, be it under construction, ready or resale property, the residence buyer can seek for loan from banks or financial institutions through financial advisors or home loan agents.\r\n\r\nIt should be noted that the terms and conditions of the housing loan can differ widely in terms of loan amount, maturity period, interest rate, repayment mode, etc.\r\n\r\nRANKPROPERTIES Consultancy has been working in this arena for several years as home loan advisors and home loan agents. We have expertise in identifying the banks and institutions that offer the loan on most friendly terms. Till date, we have been instrumental and successful home loan advisors in Mumbai providing home loans to salaried individuals, self employed, professionals and NRIs to procure home loans at best terms.\r\n\r\nOur home loan advisors strive to provide you the home loan deals at the cheapest rate of interest.\r\n\r\n<strong>Home loans to</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Salaried Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Self Employed Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Individual</li>\r\n	<li>NRI\'s</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Loan amount &amp; Loan Tenure</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>From 10 Lacs to 10 Crore</li>\r\n	<li>Decided on Market Value of Property</li>\r\n	<li>Decided on repaying capacity of the borrower basis income documents</li>\r\n	<li>5 yrs to 15/20 yrs – for Self Employed</li>\r\n	<li>5 yrs to 20/25 yrs – for professional &amp; Salaried</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Mortgage Loan</strong>\r\n\r\nMortgage loan or loan against property means the borrower takes a loan which is secured against his current residential or commercial property. The benefit of mortgage loan is that it considers the market value of the property as on date. As such, the borrower can get higher amounts of loan. Best is, the loan money can be used to meet financials requirements of any kind.\r\n\r\n<strong>Loan Against Property to</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Salaried Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Self Employed Individual</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Individual</li>\r\n	<li>NRI\'s</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Why loan against property?</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Working capital requirement</li>\r\n	<li>To fill short term financial requirement</li>\r\n	<li>Business Expansion</li>\r\n	<li>To set up new business</li>\r\n	<li>Debt Consolidation</li>\r\n	<li>Home Extension or Renovation</li>\r\n	<li>Marriage, Travel or Education</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Property Loan Consultant','','inherit','closed','closed','','170-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 11:00:58','2015-12-18 11:00:58','',170,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/170-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(256,1,'2015-12-18 11:01:54','2015-12-18 11:01:54','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Property Loan Consultant\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]\r\n<h3><strong>Property Loan Consultant:</strong></h3>\r\nThe property prices are always sky-rocketing in Andhra Pradesh if you don’t have funds to buy the property you want, availing Property loans is a good option. We are a Andhra Pradesh based credible Property Loan Consultant and have links with financial institutions like ICICI bank, HDF