rvice. Based in Chennai and Coimbatore, our company offers a multitude of services which ranges from commercial, residential and even retail spaces. We have a professional group, comprised of men and women in the property management industry who have an extensive knowledge and experience in the field. We make use of our group’s talents and commitment to help the individuals in India, making sure that as our clients, they are happy and secured about the status of their properties.\r\n\r\nThe driving force behind our company is our genuine desire to help NRI’s as they invest in properties that they cannot see to personally. We understand the difficulties involved in owning a space that you cannot manage personally – either because you have decided to reside in another territory permanently or you are temporarily living in another area to make sure that your children is getting the highest quality in education. Rest assured that we at Rankproperties Management Services are very capable of handling your investments.\r\n\r\nAside from our professional team, we also take great pride in the wide range of services that we offer. We know the property management industry likes the back of our hands. And as such, we are very capable of bringing you the wide range of services. We are not only equipped to help you save time because everything you need for your property management requirements is made available through our company. We are also a reputable company and we have earned our good name by offering cost-effective services to satisfied clients.\r\n\r\n<strong>We specialize in</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Property Management</li>\r\n	<li>New Construction</li>\r\n	<li>Tenant Management</li>\r\n	<li>Rental Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Property Monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>Refurbishing</li>\r\n	<li>Real Estate Buying &amp; Selling</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Why Seek a Property Management Service Provider?</strong>\r\n\r\nAn NRI who is interested in investing on a piece of land in his or her own country nowadays deal with a lot of complexities. At this point, there are many difficulties encountered such as the challenging affairs the need to be settled about properties in India, the actual work of managing properties – especially I these properties are for lease and even the paperwork that comes with managing a property. All of these complexities make it necessary to find someone whom you can entrust your properties to. Although relatives can help in keeping an eye on the property, they may not be fully-equipped to handle the entire property management requirements for the upkeep of your investment.\r\n\r\n<strong>Why Choose Rankproperties Management Services?</strong>\r\n\r\nEvery company offers exclusive perks and privileges to their clients. take a look at what we can offer you at Rankproperties Management Services:\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Professional team</strong>\r\n\r\nOur team is comprised of men who are trained to handle property management requirements. They were also engaged in a number of trainings seminars to further enhance their knowledge and experience in dealing with property management dealings. More than anything else, our teams are also very capable of handling the most tedious paperworks for the purpose of managing your investment.\r\n\r\n<strong>2. NRI background</strong>\r\n\r\nThe people behind the Rankproperties Management Services Company knows how it is to be an NRI because they have experienced it on their own. This makes them more equipped to handle complex issues regarding property management. Moreover, they are also able to fully understand the impact of owning an investment in India as an NRI because they were also in the same situation before.\r\n\r\n<strong>3. Reliable and cost-effective services</strong>\r\n\r\nThe services we offer at Rankproperties Management Services are reliable because we know the process that is involved when it comes to property investment and management in India. Because of what we know about the situation, we can make sure that our team can cater more to the specific needs of our clients. Our status as a reputable company in the property management industry is also a good indication of what we can do for your investment. On top of our reliable services, we are also committed to serving our clients without bleeding them dry. This is why we are offering high-quality services for a cost-effective price.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Property Managment','','inherit','closed','closed','','48-revision-v1','','','2015-12-21 14:18:10','2015-12-21 14:18:10','',48,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/48-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(306,1,'2015-12-22 05:01:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00',' ','','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2015-12-22 05:01:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/?p=306',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(307,1,'2015-12-22 05:06:15','2015-12-22 05:06:15','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Rental property management\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 class=\"left10Space top20Space\">Step-by-Step Guide to Renting Property</h2>\r\n<span class=\"positionLeft left10Space top10Space normalText\">A step-by-step guide to each stage of renting a property. </span>\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-1 Decide What You Need</h3>\r\nDiscuss with us your need and then we shall suggest you options. You can call us or email us or register your requirement over our website www.lisahomesolutions.com. We will assign a sales person on your lead and he will start showing you the property as per your choice.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-2 Property Visit</h3>\r\nSet your appointment and visit preselected properties with the sales person. Ask questions and get all relevant details about the locality, society, demographics etc. Details about schools, shopping complex, bus routes etc should also be given due importance. So clarify these entire questions before finally making an offer to the landlord.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-3 Consider Managed Prp</h3>\r\nAlso consider LHS Managed properties while making a final decision. Managed properties come with some inbuilt benefits like Service Request support, ready help and most of all you don’t have to vacate the premises every 11 months (which is very frequent practise in open market to generate brokerage) nor you need to pay hefty brokerage to renew the lease\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-4 Finalize Your Home</h3>\r\nAfter visiting the rental property let us know your selection and then we will negotiate with the landlord and get you the best possible offer.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-5 Sign the Deal Form</h3>\r\nIn case you want something to be done on the premises like new fans, tubes, geysers or whatever you wish for, write it all down in the Deal Form. We will then speak to the landlord and intimate him about your offer. Once he agrees to the terms and conditions you pay us a token amount to block the property for you.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-6 Complete Documentation</h3>\r\nWe will help you to complete all the Leave and License agreement and the police verification. Once the documentations are complete and you have given the rent and deposit amount, you get the keys.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content top20Space\">\r\n<h3>Step-7 Move-In</h3>\r\nNow you can move in your rental premises and stay happily. Always remember we are just a phone call away for any help\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Rental Property Management','','publish','closed','closed','','rental-property-management','','','2015-12-24 12:42:08','2015-12-24 12:42:08','',