s Rent Index (MBRI)</strong> helps users decide if it is beneficial to buy a property or stay on Rent thru a easy to use and understand index. These decisions are traditionally taken with gut feel or with guidance of a close relative / friend, leaving scope for error. MBRI helps answer the questions based on research &amp; data analysis.\r\n<strong>Who are the promoters of Rankproperties.com?</strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2015-12-22 05:08:24','2015-12-22 05:08:24','',42,'http://caltechsoft.com/rankprop/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(311,1,'2015-12-22 05:11:16','2015-12-22 05:11:16','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"About Us\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Abril%20Fatface%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]\r\n<h4><strong>What is Rankproperties.com?</strong></h4>\r\nRankproperties.com is an online property website committed towards helping users make wise and profitable decisions regarding buying, selling, renting and leasing of properties in India. Rankproperties.com provides fresh approach to its users to search for properties to buy and/or rent and lists their properties for selling and/or leasing.\r\n<h4><strong>Why the name Rankproperties.com?</strong></h4>\r\nNaming is a ritual in India as it reflects the sentiment and aspiration of the elders from the new born. When we were conceptualizing an online property website that would help buyers and sellers, the first name that came to the mind was Rankproperties.com as it is the most commonly used word among the Indian real-estate fraternity (property seekers, agents and builders). Most Indians also refer to their dream house as \"Rankproperties\".\r\n<h4><strong>What do we promise?</strong></h4>\r\nRankproperties.com promises to be the most pr